{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-antv-gatsby-theme-antv-0-10-14-antv-gatsby-theme-antv-site-templates-document-tsx","path":"/en/docs/specification/components/graphic","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"AntV","githubUrl":"https://github.com/antvis","docs":[{"slug":"specification/principles","title":{"zh":"设计原则","en":"Design Principles"},"order":0},{"slug":"specification/components","title":{"zh":"图表组件设计指引","en":"Design for Components of Charts"},"order":1}]},"pathPrefix":""},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"定义\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\" aria-label=\"定义 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>定义</h2>\n<p>提示信息 Tooltip，指当鼠标悬停在图表上或者手指点按移动设备的某个数据点时，<strong>以交互提示</strong>信息的形式展示该点的数据，比如该点的值，数据单位等。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"何时使用\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%95%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"何时使用 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>何时使用</h2>\n<p>当你希望数据可视化作品对用户的操作有所反馈时，提示信息 Tooltip 就可以发挥作用。<br />例如：当用户悬停一个数据点时，如果仅数据点样式发生变化而没有其他任何提示，这看起来就像一个 Bug，建议同步显示提示信息 Tooltip 帮助用户深入了解数据点的详情。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"元素\"><a href=\"#%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0\" aria-label=\"元素 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>元素</h2>\n<p>Tooltip 的基本元素包括：视觉标记图形，文本标签，数值标记等。 <br />Tooltip 的可选元素：所在的 UI 容器还可以和其他 UI 组件配合使用，完成过滤，下钻等自助分析功能。</p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/basement_prod/0677c002-9804-4d12-9d3f-744ec5d3c763.svg' width=750/>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"类型\"><a href=\"#%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\" aria-label=\"类型 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>类型</h2>\n<p>提示信息 Tooltip 按不同的图表类型，常见有如下四种：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>跟随显示的浮层提示</th>\n<th>与图例组合显示的提示</th>\n<th>与轴组合显示的提示</th>\n<th>图形上显示的提示</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>悬浮</td>\n<td>固定位置</td>\n<td>固定在轴上</td>\n<td>固定在图形上</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*jWBiQa_9An0AAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=243/></td>\n<td><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*863pQ7Uw3y8AAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/></td>\n<td>[<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*DB8JTaxMB3sAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=292/></td>\n<td><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*qjY2Sp_5kCwAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=350/></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"跟随显示的浮层提示\"><a href=\"#%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%8F%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%AE%E5%B1%82%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\" aria-label=\"跟随显示的浮层提示 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>跟随显示的浮层提示</h3>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*I-40QY9l0qsAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<p><strong>适合设备：</strong>PC 端<br /><strong>出现位置：</strong>悬浮即触发显示，跟随鼠标移动<br /><strong>适合图表类型：</strong>全部图表</p>\n<h3 id=\"与图例组合显示的提示\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%8E%E5%9B%BE%E4%BE%8B%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\" aria-label=\"与图例组合显示的提示 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>与图例组合显示的提示</h3>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*YzfWTYhikzYAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<p><strong>适合设备：</strong>常用于移动端，PC 端也适用<br /><strong>出现位置：</strong>图表上方<br /><strong>适合图表类型：</strong>全部图表</p>\n<h3 id=\"与轴组合显示的提示\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%8E%E8%BD%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\" aria-label=\"与轴组合显示的提示 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>与轴组合显示的提示</h3>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*iiTwS5EqJ94AAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<p><strong>适合设备：</strong>常用于 PC 端，移动端也可使用<br /><strong>出现位置：</strong>轴上，覆盖轴标签<br /><strong>适合图表类型：</strong>散点图、气泡图等迪卡尔坐标系图表</p>\n<h3 id=\"图形上显示的提示\"><a href=\"#%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%E4%B8%8A%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\" aria-label=\"图形上显示的提示 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>图形上显示的提示</h3>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*q7hcQYsi6NsAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<p><strong>适合设备：</strong>PC 端、移动端均可<br /><strong>出现位置：</strong>图形上<br /><strong>适合图表类型：</strong>环图</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/graphic/#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\">定义</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/graphic/#%E4%BD%95%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\">何时使用</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/graphic/#%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0\">元素</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/graphic/#%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\">类型</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/graphic/#%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%8F%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%AE%E5%B1%82%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\">跟随显示的浮层提示</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/graphic/#%E4%B8%8E%E5%9B%BE%E4%BE%8B%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\">与图例组合显示的提示</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/graphic/#%E4%B8%8E%E8%BD%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\">与轴组合显示的提示</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/graphic/#%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%E4%B8%8A%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\">图形上显示的提示</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/graphic","readingTime":{"text":"1 min read","time":34500}},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tooltip"},"parent":{"relativePath":"specification/components/graphic.en.md"}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/basic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Principles","order":0}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/basic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"设计原则","order":0}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/visual"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Visual","order":1}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/visual"},"frontmatter":{"title":"视觉","order":1}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/interact"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Interact","order":2}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/interact"},"frontmatter":{"title":"交互","order":2}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/titlenotes"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Title and Notes","order":3}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/titlenotes"},"frontmatter":{"title":"标题与注释","order":3}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/mobile"},"frontmatter":{"title":"移动","order":3}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/mobile"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Mobile","order":3}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/axis"},"frontmatter":{"title":"轴","order":4}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/axis"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Axis","order":4}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/legend"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Legend","order":5}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/legend"},"frontmatter":{"title":"图例","order":5}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/label"},"frontmatter":{"title":"标签","order":6}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/label"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Label","order":6}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/graphic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tooltip","order":7}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/tooltip"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tooltip","order":7}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/tooltip"},"frontmatter":{"title":"提示信息","order":7}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/graphic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"图形设计指引","order":8}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/resources"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Resource Download","order":10}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/resources"},"frontmatter":{"title":"资源下载","order":10}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/reference"},"frontmatter":{"title":"经典文献","order":11}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/reference"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Classical Literature","order":11}}}]}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"prev":{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/axis"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Axis","order":4},"html":"<h2 id=\"定义\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\" aria-label=\"定义 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>定义</h2>\n<p>二维空间里统计图表中的轴，是用来定义坐标系中数据在方向和值的映射关系的图表组件。</p>\n<h2 id=\"何时使用\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%95%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"何时使用 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>何时使用</h2>\n<p>在二维笛卡尔坐标系中，轴通常为水平方向的横轴（x 轴）和竖直方向的纵轴（y 轴）。极坐标系中，轴分为切向的切向轴（angle）和径向轴（radius）。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"元素\"><a href=\"#%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0\" aria-label=\"元素 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>元素</h2>\n<p>轴的元素包括：轴线、轴刻度线、轴标签和轴标题和坐标网格线。</p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*o8XoSJZQRDcAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"类型\"><a href=\"#%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\" aria-label=\"类型 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>类型</h2>\n<p>映射轴的数据类型可分为<br /><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*OcosRYoYmDAAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=746/></p>\n<p>对应地，轴可以分为：分类轴，时间轴，连续轴。<br />示例<br /><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*zc8XRKCr4hEAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/></p>\n<hr>\n<p><a name=\"uVw7l\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"轴标题\"><a href=\"#%E8%BD%B4%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98\" aria-label=\"轴标题 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>轴标题</h2>\n<p><strong>何时使用：</strong>使用文本来描述当前轴标签数据的意义<br /><strong>设计建议：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>通常都建议加上轴标题解释轴的含义。当图表其他部分的内容（图表标题，图形标签，注释，轴标签文字等）已能充分显示轴的意义，可以略去轴标题，精简画面元素。</li>\n<li>除了数值百分比（%），科学计数法单位（k/m/g）、日期时间（年/月/日）单位和其他情况的数据单位建议在轴标题中显示，在各个轴标签中略去。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>例：</strong>生产总值（亿元）<br /><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*LL6zQ6sIxwQAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/></p>\n<h2 id=\"轴标签\"><a href=\"#%E8%BD%B4%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE\" aria-label=\"轴标签 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>轴标签</h2>\n<p><strong>响应式设计建议：</strong><br />可根据图表类型设置轴标签是否显示、旋转角度以及显示间隔。<br />对文本数据：不建议开启抽样。<br />对数值数据：不建议开启尾部省略。</p>\n<p><strong>默认方案：</strong><br />连续轴、时间轴默认自动抽样 + 不旋转；分类轴默认自动旋转 + 自动省略。<br /><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*Ii5XTb5oHIUAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/></p>\n<h2 id=\"元素的显示策略\"><a href=\"#%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E7%9A%84%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5\" aria-label=\"元素的显示策略 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>元素的显示策略</h2>\n<p><strong>设计建议：</strong><br />轴上所有的元素可根据图表类型设置不同的显示策略。</p>\n<p><strong>1、折线、面积图为例</strong><br /><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*Zs9-TJkZv_4AAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/></p>\n<p><strong>2、柱状图为例</strong><br /> <img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*vTqLQrv26eAAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/><br /></p>\n<p><strong>3、条形图为例</strong><br /> <img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*_lFeTbo1gEgAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/><br /></p>\n<p><strong>4、散点图为例</strong><br /> <img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*HDcFQrOvMVUAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/><br /></p>\n<p><strong>另外：</strong> <br />上面 4 个设计建议中提到的，轴标签「若图形区域内有数据标签」，则轴标签可以考虑隐藏，如下图： <br /><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*C2QwTo41DyUAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/></p>\n<h2 id=\"数据格式\"><a href=\"#%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"数据格式 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>数据格式</h2>\n<p>在轴的使用中，往往离不开对数据的展示，在格式上我们有以下设计建议，引导用户采取正确的数据格式。</p>\n<h3 id=\"数值\"><a href=\"#%E6%95%B0%E5%80%BC\" aria-label=\"数值 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>数值</h3>\n<p>数值是用来表示计量事物的符号。根据业务诉求，数字可单独出现或搭配数字符号进行使用。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>符号格式</th>\n<th>如何使用及何时使用</th>\n<th>例子</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>千分位</td>\n<td>默认使用千分位帮助用户阅读。</td>\n<td>123,220</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>计量单位</td>\n<td>计量单位默认用小写字母。</td>\n<td>123,220kg</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>百分比</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>12.32%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>正斜杠</td>\n<td>用分数的形式表示事物的进展。</td>\n<td>12/30</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"金额\"><a href=\"#%E9%87%91%E9%A2%9D\" aria-label=\"金额 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>金额</h3>\n<p><strong>小写金额</strong>的规范是「货币符号+数字」的格式，例如“CNY1,123.00\"。<br />货币符号（<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%B4%A7%E5%B8%81%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81/7467182?fr=aladdin\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"nofollow\">货币符号表</a>）就是用来表示货币的符号，分为字母和字符两种：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>货币符号</th>\n<th>如何使用及何时使用</th>\n<th>例子</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>字符</td>\n<td>以人民币为例，金额前带货币单位标志「¥」。</td>\n<td>¥123.00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>字母</td>\n<td>以人民币为例，推荐使用  CNY ，CNY  为国际上通用的货币代码。</td>\n<td>CNY123.00</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>特殊情况</strong><br />1.如果一个数值很大，那么数值中的“万”“亿”单位可采用汉字。</p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*fXJqRrk0bNUAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=744/>\n<h3 id=\"日期与时间\"><a href=\"#%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%9F%E4%B8%8E%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4\" aria-label=\"日期与时间 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>日期与时间</h3>\n<p><strong>绝对时间</strong><br />针对用户对时间的精确度要求较高，强调信息发布的具体精确时间点有需要回顾过去的内容并通过绝对时间用来检索信息的诉求。</p>\n<p>日期可以通过以下方式格式化：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>格式</th>\n<th>如何使用及何时使用</th>\n<th>例子</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>年、月、日</td>\n<td>中国默认使用「yyyy-mm-dd」格式。（<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%90%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%9F%E5%92%8C%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E6%B3%95\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"nofollow\">其它国家参考链接）</a></td>\n<td>2019-12-08</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>专用名词</td>\n<td>含有月日的专用名词采用阿拉伯数字表示时，应采用间隔号「·」将月、日分开，并在数字前后加引号。</td>\n<td>“6.1 儿童节”</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>日期范围</td>\n<td>在日期或时间范围之间显示一个波浪号 （前后需要空格）</td>\n<td>2018-12-08 ～ 2019-12-07</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>默认使用二十四小时制：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>时间制</th>\n<th>如何使用及何时使用</th>\n<th>例子</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>二十四小时制</td>\n<td>二十四小时时间格式  HH:mm:ss 。</td>\n<td>14:08:00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>十二小时制</td>\n<td>十二小时时间格式 h:mm:ss 。</td>\n<td>2:08:00 PM<br />2:08:00 AM</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>日期时间规范：<br />日期与时间在一起展示时，用「空格」分割开，如“2019-12-08 06:00:00”。</p>\n<p><strong>相对时间</strong><br />相对时间的精确度对于用户并不十分重要，重要的是信息的即时性。在中后台中，相对时间一般用于消息、通知类功能，用户往往更关注于书面形式的时间单位，而不必去往前推算出发布的具体时间点。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>时间</th>\n<th>展示形式</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1 分钟以内的时间</td>\n<td>刚刚</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1 小时以内的时间</td>\n<td>N 分钟前</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>24 小时以内的时间</td>\n<td>N 小时前</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>24 小时以外的时间</td>\n<td>用 mm-dd HH:mm 的形式表示，即「12-08 08:00」</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>超过一年的时间</td>\n<td>用 yyyy-mm-dd HH:mm 的形式表示，即「2019-12-08 08:00」</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"数据状态\"><a href=\"#%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81\" aria-label=\"数据状态 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>数据状态</h3>\n<p><strong>无数据</strong><br />无数据用「--」表述。</p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*XdDkQ4nIJ5IAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"常见问题\"><a href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\" aria-label=\"常见问题 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>常见问题</h2>\n<h3 id=\"双轴图的轴如何设计？\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%8C%E8%BD%B4%E5%9B%BE%E7%9A%84%E8%BD%B4%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%9F\" aria-label=\"双轴图的轴如何设计？ permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>双轴图的轴如何设计？</h3>\n<p>在企业级产品中，往往遇到的一个课题是「如何在有限的空间内，传递更多信息」。<br />虽然从设计的角度更建议使用两个独立的图表来传递信息，但我们的用户往往喜欢使用双轴图解决这个场景。</p>\n<p><strong>设计建议</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>尽量保证基线从「0」开始</li>\n<li>建议两组数据的 Y 轴单位是不同的，比如一组为「人数」，一组为「百分比」</li>\n<li>警惕：<strong>由于双轴图表的刻度不受限制，因此可能使读者误读两组数据之间的关系。</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>例：<br /><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*s0xhQZmQMH8AAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/></p>"}},"next":{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/legend"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Legend","order":5},"html":"<h2 id=\"定义\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\" aria-label=\"定义 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>定义</h2>\n<p>图例解释了图表区域中包含的所有视觉元素的含义。</p>\n<h2 id=\"何时使用\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%95%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"何时使用 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>何时使用</h2>\n<p>对图表中的图形进行解释说明，用来<strong>映射图形的尺寸、颜色、数值大小</strong>等含义，帮助用户直观地理解图表。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"元素\"><a href=\"#%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0\" aria-label=\"元素 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>元素</h2>\n<p>由映射图形形状 + 文本组成。</p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*cuBUSJcvI9IAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<h2 id=\"类型\"><a href=\"#%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\" aria-label=\"类型 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>类型</h2>\n<p>根据数据类型不同，分为<strong>连续型图例</strong>和<strong>分类型图例</strong>。<br />根据状态不同，图例可以被设置为<strong>静态</strong>或可<strong>交互态</strong>。</p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*2lZfQYFzLfYAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"常见问题\"><a href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\" aria-label=\"常见问题 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>常见问题</h2>\n<h3 id=\"问题-1：如何决定图例的位置？\"><a href=\"#%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98-1%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E5%9B%BE%E4%BE%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%9F\" aria-label=\"问题 1：如何决定图例的位置？ permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>问题 1：如何决定图例的位置？</h3>\n<p>图例是对图形本身的概括。通常人的视觉动线是从上至下，从左到右。默认把图例放在左上角去做一个通用的方案看起来没毛病。<br />但更好的做法是：<strong>缩短用户对照图例看图形的本能路径，提升信息获取效率。</strong><br /><strong><br /></strong><br /><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*mE-5QbrfhNsAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/><br /><strong><br />虽然图例的位置从技术上支持了 12 个位置，我们总结了图例在不同的图表类型中不同的位置后，经过克制收敛为两类，并应用在 plot 图表类库中，以及智能生成图表工具中。<br /></strong>设计者和观看者甚至并不会感知到位置的变化，但是对应图形获取信息的效率就在不经意间提升了。<strong><br /></strong><br /><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*uuHERrMiBTUAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=500/></p>\n<h3 id=\"问题-2：图例太多怎么办？\"><a href=\"#%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98-2%EF%BC%9A%E5%9B%BE%E4%BE%8B%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E%EF%BC%9F\" aria-label=\"问题 2：图例太多怎么办？ permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>问题 2：图例太多怎么办？</h3>\n<p>在 g2plot 中，图例如果占据了图表大部分的位置，你可以发现我们提供了翻页功能。</p>"}}}}}